naanal ( தமிழ் : நாணல் , english : tall grass or reed ) is a 1965 black-and-white tamil family drama film directed by k. balachandar and produced by g. n. saravanan .   the script was written by k. balachandar and music by v. kumar .   it stars r. muthuraman , major sundararajan , sreekanth , sowcar janaki , k. r. vijaya and nagesh .   when crazy mohan wrote his first play for s. v. sekhar 's troupe , he was inspired by naanal to create crazy thieves in palavakkam .